Class MaplyTileID

  com.mousebirdconsulting.maply.MaplyTileID

java.lang.Comparable<MaplyTileID>
public class MaplyTileID
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<MaplyTileID>

A tile ID represents a single tile for paging. Tile IDs will show up when you're implementing a tile source. You'll be given a tileID to fetch the data for.

We assume all tiles refer to positions with a quad tree starting at (0,0,0).
